With the release of Eclipse 3.7 the SWT team added support for __touch__ events and limited support for gestures. Gesture support can be a bit tricky. So much that scientists develop "intricate algorithms":http://vub.academia.edu/BeatSigner/Papers/88526/iGesture_A_Java_Framework_for_the_Development_and_Deployment_of_Stroke-Based_Online_Gesture_Recognition_Algorithms to handle them. 